column2: BRIEF-Great Western Bancorp Sets Quarterly Cash Dividend Of $0.25 Per Share April 26 (Reuters) - Great Western Bancorp Inc: * GREAT WESTERN BANCORP, INC. DECLARES INCREASED QUARTERLY CASH DIVIDEND * GREAT WESTERN BANCORP - NEW QUARTERLY DIVIDEND REPRESENTS INCREASE OF 25.0% COMPARED TO MOST RECENT QUARTERLY DIVIDEND OF $0.20 PER COMMON SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
